{"tid":317883,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖四年 比人帽左兩年","createTime":"2017-07-11T17:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T18:25:38.000Z","uid":126058,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a841ee10c4b90b746c8d6be6aa1e87bd3115833","tid":317883,"uid":126058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:56:22.000Z","msg":"比足空間對方，選擇相信對方，一句話厭倦，淡，破壞四年感情。<br />\n<br />\n原來係相信對方的同時，已經綠緊帽，仲要帽足兩年懵然不知，同時亦被對方話自己不是。當我以爲自己有好多不足，打算改過，同時比時間令大家重捨愛意的時間。對方已經玩到唔識返屋企。<br />\n<br />\n頹足兩個月，突然醒覺，原來對方已經唔愛自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝二奶永遠無好結果"},{"pid":"0040772a053abb003a7f49924743b5f4b47cc5c2","tid":317883,"uid":120034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝二奶生念珠菌生死"},{"pid":"3c858f47f4906870b4fb8fc874e34773929290ae","tid":317883,"uid":20134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:14:48.000Z","msg":"祝變心者死"},{"pid":"79d8e1210a3d173871d58793fff8bf7402f36d79","tid":317883,"uid":48222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:19:08.000Z","msg":"一腳踏兩船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢d真係正仆街黎，實有報應"},{"pid":"967f6658301ed33825aa0bf33d8840c346664d20","tid":317883,"uid":126058,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:24:49.000Z","msg":"唔明點解要差隻腳去人哋嘅感情 破壞人哋嘅感情 會有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34bc110769985372a04da3e97e91aee692048ff5","tid":317883,"uid":107123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:25:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>祝變心者死</blockquote>"}]}